    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the architecture and solutions of using virtual Customer Edge (vCE) of BGP IP MPLS VPN. The solution is aimed at providing efficient service delivery capability through CE virtualization, and is especially beneficial in virtual Private Cloud (vPC) environments for extending BGP/MPLS IP VPN into tenant virtual Data Center containers.</t>
